Manchester United complete the signing of Paul Pogba on a five-year deal from Juventus for a world record transfer fee of £89m (€105m), making Pogba the most expensive football player ever. (BBC Sport)In tennis, American defending champion Serena Williams defeats Angelique Kerber of Germany in straight sets to win her seventh Wimbledon Championships title and her 22nd Grand Slam title, tying the Open era record held by Steffi Graf. (BBC)